### Set your base URL here
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000

### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Public products list
# curl http://localhost:4000/api/products
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products

### Product by slug
# curl http://localhost:4000/api/products/test-product
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/test-product

### Me (requires Supabase access token)
# curl -H "Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN" http://localhost:4000/api/auth/me
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Vendor: my profile (requires token with VENDOR role)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/vendors/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Vendor: create product
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Product",
  "slug": "test-product",
  "priceCents": 1999,
  "currency": "USD"
}

### Orders: mine
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
